  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <lg xml:id="TolC261">
          <l>teḷivi ṉēyuñ ciṟappi ṉōvu</l>
          <l>maḷapi ṉeṭutta vicaiya veṉpa.</l>
        </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Iḷampūraṇar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Namaccivāya Mutaliyār</persName> 1931, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZMelJhy.TVA_BOK_0007521/page/163/mode/1up">163</ref>.</p>
      <p>
iccūttiram eṉnutaliṟṟō veṉiṉ, mēṟ kūṟip pōnta ēkāra ōkāraṅkaḷiṉ vēṟupāṭu kaṇṭu, īṇṭu uṇarttutal nutaliṟṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
varalāṟu:
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC261-Ilam-cit1">
        <l>‘nīyēe koṇṭāy’</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC261-Ilam-cit2">
        <l>‘ōo periyaṉ’</l>
      </lg>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <head>Cēṉāvaraiyar</head>
        <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Ci. Vai. Tamōtarampiḷḷai</persName> 1868, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/tolkppiyamcollat00unse/page/n214/mode/1up">211</ref>.</p>
      <p>
i-ḷ. teḷiviṉkaṇ varum ēkāramuñ ciṟappiṉkaṇ varum ōkāramum aḷapāṉ mikka icaiyaiyuṭaiyaveṉṟu colluvar āciriyar. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
aḷapeṭaiyāy varutal mēṟkāṭṭappaṭṭaṉavaṟṟuḷḷum piṟāṇṭuṅkaṇṭukoḷka.	(13)
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Nacciṉārkkiṉiyar</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">ed. <persName xml:lang="ta">Irāma. Kōvintacāmipiḷḷai</persName> 1997, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/292/mode/1up">292</ref>–<ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZM3kZpy.TVA_BOK_0008472/page/293/mode/1up">293</ref>.</p>
      <p>
itu, ēkāra vōkāraṅkaṭkup puṟanaṭai kūṟukiṉṟatu.
      </p>
      <p>
(i-ḷ) teḷiviṉ ēyuñ ciṟappi ṉōvu maḷapiṉeṭutta vicaiya veṉpa ― muṟkūṟiya teḷiviṉkaṇ varumēkāramuñ ciṟappiṉkaṇ varumōkāramu miraṇṭu māttiraiyiṉ mikka mūṉṟu māttiraiyiṉaiyuṭaiya veṉṟu kūṟuvarāciriya reṉṟavāṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
(u-m)
      </p>
      <lg xml:id="TolC261-Nacc-cit1">
        <l>uṇṭēe maṟumai</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:id="TolC261-Nacc-cit2">
        <l>ōo! uvamaṉ uṟaḻviṉṟi yottatē!</l>
      </lg>
      <p>
<term xml:lang="en">(13)</term>
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
      <head>Teyvaccilaiyār</head>
      <p xml:lang="en">1929, <ref target="https://archive.org/details/dli.jZY9lup2kZl6TuXGlZQdjZU1k0My.TVA_BOK_0007188/page/n180/mode/1up">173</ref>.</p>
      <p>
ituvumatu.
      </p>
      <p>
i-ḷ: ― tēṟṟēkāramum, ciṟappiṉvarum ōkāramum aḷapeṭai peṟṟu varum eṉṟu colluvar. e-ṟu.
      </p>
      <p>
utāraṇam mēṟkāṭṭappaṭṭatu.	[13]
      </p>
    </body>
  </text>
